des: "These cookies are made quickly with only 5 ingredients.  You can also create your own version with different flavored cake mixes and baking chips."
ins:
Combine all ingredients in the order given.  (Do not use mixer.)  Drop by teaspoon onto an ungreased cookie sheet.
Bake at 350 degrees F (175 degrees C)  for about 7 minutes.  Do not let them get brown around the edges!  Cool on the cookie sheet at least 10 minutes before trying to remove them, they will break!
